The '''British Open'''  is the Open Championship men's golf tournament.'''British Open''' may also refer to:* Women's British Open of golf* The Wimbledon Championships of tennis* British Open Show Jumping Championships* British Open Squash Championships* British Open (snooker), a now defunct tournament* British Open Wheelchair Championships a wheelchair tennis tournament that is part of the ITF super series* BDO British Open, one of the oldest competitive darts tournaments in the world* The dancing competitions of the Blackpool Dance Festivalfrom US military aircraft designator